text: I'm looking for a restaurant in the west part of town that serves German food.

I've got just the place for you! Prezzo is a great Italian restaurant located in the west part of town. You can find it at 21-24 Northampton Road, CB3 0AD. Give them a call at 01799 521260 to make a reservation. Here's your reservation number: 3456. Enjoy your meal!
